cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper focuses on improving facial attribute prediction using semantic segmentation, which is a task related to computer vision (CV). Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a joint model for attribute prediction and semantic segmentation, which involves machine learning (ML) techniques such as deep neural networks. Hence, cs.LG and cs.AI are also likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on CelebA and LFWA datasets, which are related to multimedia (MM) and information retrieval (IR). Therefore, cs.MM and cs.IR are also possible sub-categories.
